      "id": "PopularPost41840",
      "post_content": "This is given in the red deck in Duels of the Planeswalkers, and I will freely admit that there are better cards, but really, in the late game when playing red, you probably have nothing to do with all the mana on your table. This is a reusable Lava Axe. It's more expensive, sure, but this card has won games for me, believe it or not. Maybe not quite solid, but deserving of a mention. 3/5.",
